Titolo: Metal Max 2

Anno: 1993

Descrizione: Metal Max 2 (メタルマックス2) is the second entry in the Metal Max series. It was a vehicle combat RPG published in Japan by Data East in 1993 for the Super Famicom in 1993. Ten years later in 2003, the game was ported to the Game Boy Advance with a few new bounties by Now Production under the title Metal Max 2 Kai. In December 8, 2011, a full remake with upgraded graphics in the vein of Metal Max 3 and using its game engine was released in Japan for the Nintendo DS and titled Metal Max 2 Reloaded.

Genere: Role-playing video game

Valutazione: N/A
